name: Denver702.GitHub.io
body:
### Salutation viewer!
This is Denver's web page.


### This is an online brainstorming tool I made that generates random words.

It should help spark your creative imagination if you're looking to think up a domain name, a band name, a project name or whatever.

Right now it generates 6 random words by default but you can change that to generate anywhere from two to ten words.

For band names and projects, I find that setting it to three or four words gives you optimal results to work with.
